      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\">A 35-year-old man with a sedentary lifestyle is trying to adjust his diet to meet his nutritional needs. According to the 2020 guidelines from the Indian Council of Medical Research (ICMR), what is the recommended protein intake (g/kg/day) for this man?</span></p>",
